    <description>
        <p>
            mldonkey-next is a modern GUI for the multi-protocol p2p filesharing application
            mldonkey. mldonkey-next connects to mldonkey using the TCP binary interface.
        </p>
    </description>

    <launchable type="desktop-id">org.duckdns.bugfreeblog.mldonkeynext.desktop</launchable>

